short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Makes it easier to rejoin a Google Meet straight from the 'hasn't started yet' page and mutes your mic automatically.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The MeetRejoin chrome extension makes it easier to rejoin a Google Meet that hasn't started yet from the error page. Instead of having to close the tab and open the link again, this is much faster and saves you time. It also mutes your microphone and disables your webcam before you join a call.
